My favorite economic rice stall. Have been my default meal option when I'm home. Food's reasonably priced and tasty. The boss is also super generous, check out his generous gesture to the nearby community, giving free food to elderly once a month.
Food is good especially their prawn paste chicken and curry. Portion is generous and price is reasonable. Friendly boss too! Will visit again!
Food is fresh & delicious price is reasonable. Will support again.
